# CC: %?La<|...> blanks the ordinary-row background on album rows; every other
# CC: row (special rows included) gets the plain selection bar. The old grouped
# CC: multi-glyph frame for [All tracks]/[Random]/etc. was removed: its deep
# CC: %?if nesting mis-rendered on the first frames after a list change and
# CC: pushed skin_render_line's recursion near the stack limit.
%?La<|%?Lc<%Vs(invert)A%aRB>>
#
%Vl(Menu_No_Icons,9,8,14,14,8)%?La<|%?if(%LT,=,%Sx([All tracks]))<%?Lc<%Vs(invert)>b>%?if(%LT,=,%Sx([Random]))<%?Lc<%Vs(invert)>a>%?if(%LT,=,%Sx([Untagged]))<%?Lc<%Vs(invert)>e>%?if(%LT,=,%Sx([By album]))<%?Lc<%Vs(invert)>脦>>
#
